{"tid":1955894,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[大家久等了！？] 消息稱 Apple 全新平價機型 iPhone SE2 或將於 4 月正式登場","createTime":"2020-04-02T20:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T04:28:00.000Z","uid":157103,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0c6040087394c55cd1f22f3daddfbe51db93cabb","tid":1955894,"uid":157103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T20:11:10.000Z","msg":"不少人期待的 Apple 全新平價機型 iPhone SE2（iPhone 9）並未在早前 Apple 春季線上發佈活動中曝光，不過近日根據知名情報用戶 Jon Prosser 最新推文指出，iPhone SE2 或將於 4 月 15 日正式發表，並於 4 月 22 日正式發貨，不過可能因疫情有所更動，不過官方仍未對此作澄清與進行相關預告。<br />\n<br />\n過去種種消息指出， iPhone SE2 有機會推出 4.7 吋與 5.5 吋兩大型號，配色上則提供灰、銀及紅等款式，更有機會兼容 Touch ID 和 Face ID，價格約略在 $399 美金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/hypebeast.com/zh/2020/4/apple-iphone-se2-9-announce-rumor-april%3famp=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2020%2F4%2Fapple-iphone-se2-9-announce-rumor-april%253famp%3D1&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMmCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=28ec204c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/hypebeast.com/zh/2020/4/apple-iphone-se2-9-announce-rumor-april%3famp=1</a>"},{"pid":"455498f96141f84c8866445d0e030db02a5fda06","tid":1955894,"uid":322038,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T20:11:51.000Z","msg":"流浮山刀手到先 定係SE2出先?"},{"pid":"8e6b6a534661df3c4c0f91867bc8d84e8d4467eb","tid":1955894,"uid":157103,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T20:13:59.000Z","msg":"揸住SE2嘅流浮山刀手"},{"pid":"b99cb981ae924a95382884f938feaab8b71022d9","tid":1955894,"uid":286309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T20:32:04.000Z","msg":"Apple撚狗大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159f75dfde2b40ccc9272865f0265a0e73cf31be","tid":1955894,"uid":5